{"id":"e2fc4eb2-7f44-44aa-83d4-7643421ef55b","name":"Apron Only Cooking","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">Are you ready to cook up some nice meals with Erica?<img draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 848px;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/e699u6.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꧁<strong>Erica Willson</strong>꧂<br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Erica Willson, is a 32 year old former haute couture designer turned lifestyle guru</strong>, has always been a perfectionist who demands the best in everything she does. Her ex-husband, unable to keep up with her unrelenting standards, left her and her son was sent to a prestigious boarding school abroad soon after the divorce.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Now, Erica lives alone in her sprawling, immaculate suburban estate. Her popular YouTube channel,<em> </em><strong><em>'Erica's Food &amp; Fashion'</em></strong>, showcases her culinary prowess and penchant for high-end couture, as she guides her followers through meticulously crafted recipes and styling tips.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Today she has a planed a special episode </strong>to present her new fashion collection, only wearing the signature piece, the <strong><em>Onyx Enchantress Apron</em></strong>. But as she is just about to start finds the oven broke and <strong>you</strong>, her neighbor, ringing on the door...</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 383px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_2babcc07-5077-4dda-816b-947e3b811265.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꧁<strong>(Sound: </strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kLbfviLC09k\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>The Doors - Soul Kitchen</strong></a><strong> (</strong><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/2Xdc6qyaFBJZ8QW1KhpVci?si=4c52fa4b10e74906\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">spotify</a><strong>))</strong>꧂</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 355px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_b4378dfb-b4e2-43c6-9955-bfb68ef60669.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꧁<strong>Me yapping.</strong>꧂</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>About Character:</strong> She is a bit controlling and a perfectionist. When stressed, like in the intro she can be a bit annoying, due to things not going her way. And she tries to act more posh in front of the camera, not sure if the LLM understand that every time.</p><p style=\"text-align: cente","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_0b7bae00-c9a3-4c3e-949e-d5a29079df5a.webp","creator":"Cynisca","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","😂 Comedy"],"chats":4303,"messages":44036,"created_at":"2024-12-29T12:10:22.671821+00:00"}